744
00:26:49,110 --> 00:26:50,179
Yes, well...

745
00:26:50,180 --> 00:26:51,579
Only the flight time is different.

746
00:26:51,580 --> 00:26:53,389
- As I was listening, - Yes.

747
00:26:53,390 --> 00:26:56,149
It felt like I had become Min Soo.

748
00:26:56,150 --> 00:26:58,819
But why didn't she answer your messages?

749
00:26:58,820 --> 00:27:00,689
The reason she didn't answer...

750
00:27:00,690 --> 00:27:02,929
