753
00:27:06,870 --> 00:27:08,369
Yes. So...

754
00:27:08,370 --> 00:27:10,069
She was very worried...

755
00:27:10,070 --> 00:27:13,270
and was determined not to date me.

756
00:27:13,570 --> 00:27:14,739
But I kept knocking.

757
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:16,069
I kept sending her messages,

758
00:27:16,070 --> 00:27:18,710
and they say a bridge will fall down if you keep knocking at it.

759
00:27:19,040 --> 00:27:20,879
So she let down her wall.

760
00:27:20,880 --> 00:27:23,249
- A bridge won't fall if you... - Will a bridge fall if you knock?

761
00:27:23,250 --> 00:27:24,919
- That should not happen. - Is that not it?

762
00:27:24,920 --> 00:27:26,319
You need to knock on it before you cross.

763
00:27:26,320 --> 00:27:27,419
Oh, you're supposed to cross it.

764
00:27:27,420 --> 00:27:29,549
He's similar to me.

765
00:27:29,550 --> 00:27:31,759
His knowledge is similar to mine.

766
00:27:31,760 --> 00:27:34,559
I thought you were correct for a second.

767
00:27:34,560 --> 00:27:36,659
You said the bridge would fall.

768
00:27:36,660 --> 00:27:38,140
Will it fall down if you knock on it?

769
00:27:38,260 --> 00:27:39,899
Are you talking about the tree that won't stand still...

770
00:27:39,900 --> 00:27:41,829
