771
00:27:41,830 --> 00:27:42,830
- Yes, that's it. - Right?

772
00:27:42,831 --> 00:27:44,439
I struck ten times.

773
00:27:44,440 --> 00:27:45,869
You said the bridge fell down.

774
00:27:45,870 --> 00:27:48,039
So what happened when you went to Japan?

775
00:27:48,040 --> 00:27:50,840
- I went there and we met, - Yes.

776
00:27:51,080 --> 00:27:52,239
- and I suggested that we eat. - Yes.

777
00:27:52,240 --> 00:27:53,949
So we ate,

778
00:27:53,950 --> 00:27:55,449
and after eating,

779
00:27:55,450 --> 00:27:57,379
