780
00:27:57,380 --> 00:27:58,679
That's so sad.

781
00:27:58,680 --> 00:28:00,819
And then we met again the next day...

782
00:28:00,820 --> 00:28:01,820
and had coffee.

783
00:28:01,821 --> 00:28:03,659
Usually, after that,

784
00:28:03,660 --> 00:28:05,689
it's common to go somewhere else after that, right?

785
00:28:05,690 --> 00:28:07,189
She just had coffee and went home.

786
00:28:07,190 --> 00:28:08,660
- She left again? - Gosh.

787
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:12,830
So when did your wife open up to you?

788
00:28:13,130 --> 00:28:14,529
About that...

789
00:28:14,530 --> 00:28:16,599
She was on the subway with me...

790
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:19,270
