I actually told Hee Chul.

830
00:29:49,060 --> 00:29:50,499
During a shoot,

831
00:29:50,500 --> 00:29:52,959
I said, "I have a Japanese girlfriend."

832
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:54,369
"I heard you do, too."

833
00:29:54,370 --> 00:29:56,129
- Oh... - So...

834
00:29:56,130 --> 00:29:57,140
Did you?

835
00:29:57,900 --> 00:29:59,399
(Oh... Did you?)

836
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:01,740
I didn't know.

837
00:30:02,440 --> 00:30:05,409
- Oh, I... - We don't know.

838
00:30:05,410 --> 00:30:07,949
He had a Japanese girlfriend back then.

839
00:30:07,950 --> 00:30:09,809
- He did. - Yes.

840
00:30:09,810 --> 00:30:11,649
I thought he would have forgotten about that.

841
00:30:11,650 --> 00:30:13,319
- He has a good memory. - The thing is...

842
00:30:13,320 --> 00:30:14,849
You forgot about the bridge,

843
00:30:14,850 --> 00:30:15,919
