844
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:18,890
- Sure. I remember it all. - I'm curious about Joo Ho.

845
00:30:19,290 --> 00:30:22,089
He said they first met at FC Basel.

846
00:30:22,090 --> 00:30:23,090
I know that really well.

847
00:30:23,091 --> 00:30:25,099
That was your team back then in Switzerland.

848
00:30:25,100 --> 00:30:27,169
- FC Basel in Switzerland. - Yes.

849
00:30:27,170 --> 00:30:30,139
I was a soccer player in Japan,

850
00:30:30,140 --> 00:30:33,540
