854
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:43,520
She had a part-time job at FC Basel during the weekends.

855
00:30:43,850 --> 00:30:48,150
But we had no one in common back then.

856
00:30:48,290 --> 00:30:51,359
My wife traveled to Korea...

857
00:30:51,360 --> 00:30:53,259
