864
00:31:09,310 --> 00:31:10,479
- What a coincidence. - What?

865
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:11,809
- Gosh, - Really?

866
00:31:11,810 --> 00:31:13,309
Is there such a thing as destiny?

867
00:31:13,310 --> 00:31:16,449
He felt so awkward,

868
00:31:16,450 --> 00:31:18,120
so he showed her my picture...

869
00:31:18,350 --> 00:31:20,650
and said that his brother was a soccer player.

870
00:31:21,050 --> 00:31:22,250
With his broken English.

871
00:31:22,490 --> 00:31:24,089
It has to be broken.

872
00:31:24,090 --> 00:31:27,029
He told her, with his broken English,

873
00:31:27,030 --> 00:31:30,359
