874
00:31:30,360 --> 00:31:32,630
She thought he was a fan of FC Basel.

875
00:31:33,330 --> 00:31:35,099
So they parted like that.

876
00:31:35,100 --> 00:31:38,200
Anna was working during the weekend,

877
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:41,040
and my family came to see my game.

878
00:31:41,410 --> 00:31:43,610
They were in the VIP family area,

879
00:31:44,080 --> 00:31:45,739
and Anna was working there.

880
00:31:45,740 --> 00:31:46,809
That's destiny.

881
00:31:46,810 --> 00:31:50,379
My mom was trying to ask for a blanket...

882
00:31:50,380 --> 00:31:52,879
and some drinks,

883
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:54,519
but it wasn't working out well.

884
00:31:54,520 --> 00:31:56,089
My wife saw her,

885
00:31:56,090 --> 00:31:57,359
and since she knew a bit of Korean,

886
00:31:57,360 --> 00:31:58,390
