887
00:31:58,760 --> 00:32:00,189
The items she was asking for.

888
00:32:00,190 --> 00:32:03,129
Through that incident, my little sister...

889
00:32:03,130 --> 00:32:04,999
became friends with Anna,

890
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:06,330
and they kept staying in touch.

891
00:32:06,830 --> 00:32:09,369
So I just knew her as my little sister's friend...

892
00:32:09,370 --> 00:32:11,169
- for about a year. - Your sister's friend?

893
00:32:11,170 --> 00:32:12,410
Yes, my little sister's friend.

894
00:32:12,470 --> 00:32:15,340
But then, my team won,

895
00:32:15,870 --> 00:32:17,879
and we had a celebration party...

896
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:19,709
until late in the night,

897
00:32:19,710 --> 00:32:21,779
and we had a motorcycle...

898
00:32:21,780 --> 00:32:24,150
