908
00:32:46,100 --> 00:32:47,969
That's how we had our first date.

909
00:32:47,970 --> 00:32:49,169
(That's how the couple had their first date.)

910
00:32:49,170 --> 00:32:50,279
And then...

911
00:32:50,280 --> 00:32:51,739
Who wanted to go steady first?

912
00:32:51,740 --> 00:32:53,949
I think it was my wife.

913
00:32:53,950 --> 00:32:55,879
- What? - It was my wife.

914
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:57,519
We have to listen to her story, too.

915
00:32:57,520 --> 00:33:00,449
A lot of men lie like that.

916
00:33:00,450 --> 00:33:01,989
