917
00:33:01,990 --> 00:33:04,290
Listen and see if I'm right.

918
00:33:04,560 --> 00:33:07,260
For a while, we just met up sometimes...

919
00:33:07,530 --> 00:33:09,189
to have dinner and go on walks.

920
00:33:09,190 --> 00:33:11,829
But I had to keep talking in English,

921
00:33:11,830 --> 00:33:12,999
