926
00:33:24,080 --> 00:33:25,080
That is a confession.

927
00:33:25,081 --> 00:33:27,481
You should have been witty and said, "You're my girlfriend."

928
00:33:29,110 --> 00:33:30,379
So?

929
00:33:30,380 --> 00:33:32,050
