931
00:33:34,620 --> 00:33:35,719
- What did you say to her? - What did you say?

932
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:36,720
What did you say?

933
00:33:37,060 --> 00:33:39,990
"We're friends, but you're a woman,"

934
00:33:40,260 --> 00:33:41,429
