941
00:33:51,771 --> 00:33:53,539
You should have held her hand. "You're my woman!"

942
00:33:53,540 --> 00:33:55,409
(You are my woman!)

943
00:33:55,410 --> 00:33:58,310
The reason I said that back then was because...

944
00:33:58,610 --> 00:34:00,750
I had never even thought of dating a foreigner,

945
00:34:01,650 --> 00:34:04,979
